Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA为何会如此美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为何会如此美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为 大家都在心中收藏着美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 我还想继续与更多的人邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 昨天的一场雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让今天的威尼斯披上了雪白的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像为迎接即将到来的新年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给城市换上的新装一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐 AQUA很远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更深地去体会那里夏日的炎热和冬天的寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但AQUA实在太远 我一个人无法前往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的新威尼斯 一定很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 我过去也有过跟小爱一样的想法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我 是那时的我想要成为的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差不多到时间去参加共同练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:39.23,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(320,280)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 雪白的温馨城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 蓝华 香草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直温暖到心里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这雪下得还真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个晚上就积了这么厚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像新威尼斯城重生了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听到「啊～」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 灯里小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 蓝华 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们小时候想要变成什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是突然想到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能没太想过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小后辈还是小孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经不是爱哭鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已经不是爱哭鬼了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目标 果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像艾莉西亚前辈一样的优雅女性啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会被晃前辈骂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为领航员的话 我还是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但艾莉西亚前辈还是我憧憬的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要变成艾莉西亚前辈那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学别人 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你可别小看了艾莉西亚前辈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要变成那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要相当的努力和毅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗 毅力哦 毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里你没有的吧 毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在想别的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈以前想变成什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是个优雅的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们去散步吧 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积了这么厚的雪 大概不会有客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就打烊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始有点冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好暖和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖包包 送给灯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 灯里你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这条路还没有人走过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈小时候想成为什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得很大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 叔叔也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚到这么大应该够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谢不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那艾莉西亚前辈想变成什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不好意思 那个雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以加入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次滚这么大的雪球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 我玩得非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上坡路很难滚呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 要用力推哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆到哪都不会丢人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我们马上把它移走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不用不用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次见到这么大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们俩做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人都帮过忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那也让我们来帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领航员小姐们 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝点暖和的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的 好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用 很暖和的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 纯白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是白可可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用白巧克力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手一定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在做三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃点小蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要玩得太疯喊腰痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥 这个不疯怎么行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要把它弄得更大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我们再多做一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 三弹吗 不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 刚才的领航员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经滚得这么大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也在帮忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那爸爸也再来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么帮忙啊 这本来就是领航员小姐的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领航员小姐真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了就用这个来装饰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装饰装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊对了 我还有些好看的布头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是滚雪球 却能邂逅很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己被大家所温暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越来越喜欢这个城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪的时候 我总是会去滚雪球玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始滚雪球啊 总是会有人跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起帮我把雪球越滚越大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后 大家都会很满足地回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时侯啊 我突然想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想变成那样的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个微笑 就如水之精灵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这么一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了时间的流逝 看得入了迷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈果然是个美好的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你与我相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给了我这么难能可贵的邂逅的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔地守护着我的这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐 我长大以后一定要去新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候灯里姐姐一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的城市非常美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像艾莉西亚小姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 AQUA今天也很和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在感谢本大爷吗 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿帕爷爷 有人送了好吃的年糕给我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也继续在空中遨游
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要世界上还存在包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 蓝华 我们去吃披萨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 晃前辈请客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以考虑请你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 太好了 我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 总有一天我会要你加倍奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你成为正式领航员之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 天气暖和起来后 我们去野餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密 不过是个很好的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那灯里想变成什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:23:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候想要成为精灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 自由地在世界上飞舞 让大家都得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里马上也能成为精灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:46.23,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,0)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}希望 这座城市的温馨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.89,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,0)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}能够传达到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:55.46,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,2400)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}许多人的心中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:02:04.49,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:18.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:34.34,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:47.79,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:56.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:05.28,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:13.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:17.22,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:25.26,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:02:04.49,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:18.62,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:34.34,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:47.79,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:56.96,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:05.28,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:13.62,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:17.22,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:25.26,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:01.84,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}手のひらの上に そっとのせた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:09.37,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}やさしさを あたためて そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:13.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}口ずさんだ 秘密のメロヂィー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:21.24,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}歌ってよ 行くあてもないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:25.32,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}でも 降り出した雨も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:31.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}気にしない ずっとそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:40.56,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いくつもの虹 越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ふたりで オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:51.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな光 星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:57.06,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}叶えてよ きっと 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:25.05,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いくつもの虹 越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:28.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ふたりで オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:36.38,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな光 星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.79,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}叶えてよ きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:47.54,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:50.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:58.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:04.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:12.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:19.73,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:01.84,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}把悄然落在手心的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:09.37,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}细细地 温暖在怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:13.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}口中吟唱着神秘的曲调
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:21.24,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}吟唱着 失去了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:25.32,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}可是 那飘落的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:31.85,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}却不能影响我 因为有你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:40.56,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}穿过了 无数的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 一起越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:51.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一点微光 向星星许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:57.06,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鸟 定会为我实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:25.05,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}穿过了 无数的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:28.72,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 一起越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:36.38,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一点微光 向星星许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.79,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}梦想 定会实现
